OL,3,CDurham restaurant fined after allergen
OL,4,Ccontamination leaves customer in
OL,5,Chospital
OL,7,FThe owners of a Lebanese restaurant in
OL,8,FDurham have been hit with a fine of
OL,9,Fmore than #28,000 after being found
OL,10,Fguilty of allergen contamination,
OL,11,Fwhich resulted in a customer being
OL,12,Fsent to hospital.
OL,14,FDurham County Council took legal
OL,15,Faction against Lebaneat's after
OL,16,Fenvironmental health officers visited
OL,17,Fits premises on North Bailey in the
OL,18,Fcity, following a customer complaint.
