OL,3,CDurham restaurant fined after allergen
OL,4,Ccontamination leaves customer in
OL,5,Chospital
OL,7,FThe customer had requested a nut and
OL,8,Fsesame free meal, however shortly
OL,9,Fafter eating the food they suffered
OL,10,Ffrom serious anaphylaxis and had to go
OL,11,Fto hospital.
OL,13,FAn inspection of the premises found
OL,14,Fthat there were no dedicated utensils
OL,15,Ffor allergen free meals; staff were
OL,16,Fnot trained in allergens; the
OL,17,Fprocedure for preparing and serving
OL,18,Fallergen free meals were not being
OL,19,Ffollowed; and there was no dedicated
OL,20,Fmember of staff or management checking
OL,21,Fthe food orders.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/5
