OL,3,CDurham restaurant fined after allergen
OL,4,Ccontamination leaves customer in
OL,5,Chospital
OL,7,FDuring the visit, samples were taken
OL,8,Ffrom the restaurant's chicken
OL,9,Fshawarma, which was from the same
OL,10,Fbatch as the night the customer
OL,11,Fvisited.
OL,13,FThe manager, waiter and chef who were
OL,14,Fpresent on the night and involved in
OL,15,Fthe customer's food order were
OL,16,Finterviewed under caution and CCTV
OL,17,Ffootage was also examined.
OL,19,FPeterlee Magistrates Court found that
OL,20,Fthere was an intentional breach of
OL,21,Ffood safety regulations.
