OL,7,FAdam & Amin Ltd have been ordered to
OL,8,Fpay a #22,000 fine , #5,984 in costs
OL,9,Fand a #190 victim surcharge, totalling
OL,10,Fmore than #28,000.
OL,12,FIan Harrison, Durham County Council's
OL,13,Fbusiness compliance manager, said:
OL,14,F"Contamination of allergens in food is
OL,15,Fa serious health risk. Failing to
OL,16,Ffollow the right procedures to protect
OL,17,Fcustomers can result in not only them
OL,18,Fbecoming seriously ill and needing
OL,19,Fhospital treatment, but can also put
OL,20,Fcustomers' lives at risk.
