OL,7,F"It is imperative that food businesses
OL,8,Fare operating in a safe and hygienic
OL,9,Fway and in this case Lebaneat failed
OL,10,Fto ensure the safety of one of their
OL,11,Fcustomers. The severity of the fine
OL,12,Freflects just how serious we, and the
OL,13,Fcourt, take this matter and how
OL,14,Fsignificant the outcome could have
OL,15,Fbeen for this customer."
